Most single-cell analyses were performed using the environments defined in R43.yml and scpy39.yml.
Iterative clustering was conducted using the R42.yml environment.
SAMalg and SAMap analyses were run under the SAMap.yml environment.
Orthogroup analysis was performed using the WGD.yml environment.
Gene and transcription factor ranking with nsforest was carried out in the nsforest.yml environment.
pySCENIC analysis was performed using the scenicpy environment.

All software dependencies and packages can be easily installed using Conda or Mamba, with full version information documented in the corresponding .yml files.